cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.CL

The paper deals with visual content management in e-commerce, which involves image analysis and classification. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of machine learning techniques, which suggests that it could belong to cs.IR (Information Retrieval) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of deep learning and computer vision, which could place it in cs.MM (Multimedia) or cs.CL (Computation and Language).
